Agentic MM-RAG
================

This repository includes a storage-native runtime for agentic multimodal RAG.

Third-party ingestion adapters
------------------------------

The repository includes lightweight source snapshots under `data/vendor/` for
ingestion compatibility:

- `data/vendor/raganything`: RAG-Anything-compatible ingestion entrypoint code.
- `data/vendor/videorag`: VideoRAG-compatible ingestion entrypoint code.

Before publishing a public release, verify the upstream licenses for these
vendored sources and add the original copyright notices, license files, commit
references, and any required attribution. If the upstream licenses are not
compatible with redistribution, remove these vendored directories and document
installation from the upstream projects instead.

Model and data artifacts
------------------------

This repository does not include model checkpoints, processed document/video
stores, or proprietary datasets. Users must provide their own data and model
credentials.
